 @{b}with@{ub}     z, za pomocâ, np. with a knife - noűem, with difficulty - z
                   trudnoôciâ

 @{b}without@{ub}  bez, np. without a word - bez sîowa

 @{b}upon@{ub}     na, na wierzch

 @{b}without@{ub}  bez

